user_instruction: 'Tell Jane to send an email to me (info@rainbowfertility.com) with the details we need for our consultation. Ask her to check her Notion for information.'

formatted_items.content:
Hi Jane,

I hope you’re well! To help us prepare for your initial consultation, could you please send an email to info@rainbowfertility.com with the following details?

• Your and your partner’s full names (and pronouns)  
• Preferred contact information  
• A brief summary of your fertility goals and any previous treatments or evaluations  
• Preferred dates/times for an appointment  
• Any other information you’d like us to know in advance  

When you have a moment, please also check your Notion workspace—there’s a short questionnaire and some additional resources there that will guide you through the information we’ll need.

Thank you so much! We look forward to supporting you on your journey.

Warm regards,  
[Your Name]  
Rainbow Fertility Care
